        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>You spew energy from your mouth, dealing [[/r 5d6]] damage. The area, damage type, and save depend on the dragon type in your bloodline.</p>\n<h2>Dragon Breath</h2>\n<table class=\"pf2-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Dragon Type</th>\n<th>Area and damage type</th>\n<th>Saving Throw</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Copper or Black</td>\n<td>60-foot line of acid</td>\n<td>Reflex</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Blue or Bronze</td>\n<td>60-foot line of electricity</td>\n<td>Reflex</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Brass</td>\n<td>60-foot line of fire</td>\n<td>Reflex</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Green</td>\n<td>30-foot cone of poison</td>\n<td>Fortitude</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Gold or Red</td>\n<td>30-foot cone of fire</td>\n<td>Reflex</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Silver or White</td>\n<td>30-foot cone of cold</td>\n<td>Reflex</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The damage increases by [[/r 2d6]].</p>"
